  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUG BALL 3D is a top down precision platformer where you take the role of a rollie pollie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete courses as fast as you can, or take it chill and complete them at your leisure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.poster.avif?t=1729489219\" width=580 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.webm?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.mp4?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A mix of easier courses for the casual player, and gruelingly precise courses for the most committed of bug fans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A complete lack of a speed cap. How fast can you go? </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Features a unique pseudo-3D visual flare. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Modifiers that change the way you play the game. Double movement speed? A strict time limit? It's yours to choose. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable skins to make your pillbug look SWAG. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bug ! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bb26a4aaceb6ce698d96c3d5d562e5d7.poster.avif?t=1729489219\" width=542 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bb26a4aaceb6ce698d96c3d5d562e5d7.webm?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bb26a4aaceb6ce698d96c3d5d562e5d7.mp4?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/777399b2d6d0f19dbfc8cc277608597f.avif?t=1729489219\" width=250 height=150 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUG BALL 3D is a top down precision platformer where you take the role of a rollie pollie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete courses as fast as you can, or take it chill and complete them at your leisure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.poster.avif?t=1729489219\" width=580 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.webm?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bcd0fc75cc27f7b3d2d1838809e03af3.mp4?t=1729489219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A mix of easier courses for the casual player, and gruelingly precise courses for the most committed of bug fans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A complete lack of a speed cap. How fast can you go? </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Features a unique pseudo-3D visual flare. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Modifiers that change the way you play the game. Double movement speed? A strict time limit? It's yours to choose. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable skins to make your pillbug look SWAG. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bug ! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bb26a4aaceb6ce698d96c3d5d562e5d7.poster.avif?t=1729489219\" width=542 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976450/extras/bb26a4aaceb6ce698d96c3d5d562